<p><a name="Phones_with_BlackBerry_e-mail_client" id="Phones_with_BlackBerry_e-mail_client"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=BlackBerry&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13" title="Edit section: Phones with BlackBerry e-mail client">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Phones with BlackBerry e-mail client</span></h2>
<p>Several non-BlackBerry mobile phones have been released featuring the <a href="/w/index.php?title=BlackBerry_e-mail_client&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="BlackBerry e-mail client (page does not exist)">BlackBerry e-mail client</a> which connects to BlackBerry servers. Many of these phones have full QWERTY keyboards</p>
